                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000929181fa-4086-4745-b312-0c19227bd16e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(z=\frac{2+i}{1-i}=\frac{\left(2+i\right)\left(1+i\right)}{\left(1-i\right)\left(1+i\right)}=\frac{2+i+2i+{i}^{2}}{{1}^{2}-{i}^{2}}=\frac{2-1+3i}{1+1}=\frac{1}{2}+\frac{3}{2}i\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001929181fa-4086-4745-b312-0c19227bd16e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000929181fa-4086-4745-b312-0c19227bd16e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001929181fa-4086-4745-b312-0c19227bd16e {font-family: Cambria Math;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
