                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000005f099ba9-cb43-404a-a31c-3f6e29fd58f3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({x}^{4}=-169⇒{x}^{2}=±13i⇒{x}^{2}=\frac{13}{2}(±2i)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015f099ba9-cb43-404a-a31c-3f6e29fd58f3"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005f099ba9-cb43-404a-a31c-3f6e29fd58f3 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000015f099ba9-cb43-404a-a31c-3f6e29fd58f3 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cb3a79fb-4cc7-411a-864d-635392799b23" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴x=±\sqrt{\frac{13}{2}}(1±i)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cb3a79fb-4cc7-411a-864d-635392799b23"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cb3a79fb-4cc7-411a-864d-635392799b23 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001cb3a79fb-4cc7-411a-864d-635392799b23 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f537505c-416c-4b06-83b2-3318b28cc587" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001f537505c-416c-4b06-83b2-3318b28cc587">†</span><span class="pt-000001f537505c-416c-4b06-83b2-3318b28cc587">hvMdj</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f537505c-416c-4b06-83b2-3318b28cc587"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\sqrt{\frac{13}{2}}\left(1+i\right)+\sqrt{\frac{13}{2}}\left(1-i\right)-\sqrt{\frac{13}{2}}\left(1+i\right)-\sqrt{\frac{13}{2}}\left(1-i\right)=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f537505c-416c-4b06-83b2-3318b28cc587"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f537505c-416c-4b06-83b2-3318b28cc587 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f537505c-416c-4b06-83b2-3318b28cc587 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 3 </span>
