                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000b9ca2d7c-f6d8-467e-8daf-a12bad10e4ce" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left.\begin{matrix}\sqrt{x+iy}=±\frac{\sqrt{r+x}+i\sqrt{r-x}}{\sqrt{2}}\\\sqrt{x-iy}=±\frac{\sqrt{r+x}-i\sqrt{r-x}}{\sqrt{2}}\\\end{matrix}\right\}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b9ca2d7c-f6d8-467e-8daf-a12bad10e4ce"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b9ca2d7c-f6d8-467e-8daf-a12bad10e4ce {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b9ca2d7c-f6d8-467e-8daf-a12bad10e4ce {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919">†</span><span class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919">hLv</span><span class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919">‡</span><span class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919">b</span><span class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919">,</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(r=\sqrt{{x}^{2}+{y}^{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919">Ges </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y&gt;0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f71d9649-2e57-4f84-a9ca-cff3f81a5919 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f71d9