html"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=±\frac{\sqrt{5+\left(-3\right)}-i\sqrt{5-\left(-3\right)}}{\sqrt{2}}=±\frac{\sqrt{2}-i\sqrt{8}}{\sqrt{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ad33943a-0e63-446d-9de8-cb75644c0a1d"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ad33943a-0e63-446d-9de8-cb75644c0a1d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ad33943a-0e63-446d-9de8-cb75644c0a1d {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b6d554d4-1676-4614-88a5-e469afc4496b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=±\frac{\sqrt{2}-2\sqrt{2}i}{\sqrt{2}}=±\left(\frac{\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{2}}-\frac{2\sqrt{2}i}{\sqrt{2}}\right)=±\left(1-2i\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b6d554d4-1676-4614-88a5-e469afc4496b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b6d554d4-1676-4614-88a5-e469afc4496b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b6d554d4-1676-4614-88a5-e469afc4496b {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007aaf87f1-fca8-479c-a499-c4d2debc794f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000017aaf87f1-fca8-479c-a499-c4d2debc794f">weK&#237;</span><span class="pt-0000017aaf87f1-fca8-479c-a499-c4d2debc794f">:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017aaf87f1-fca8-479c-a499-c4d2debc794f"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(-3-4i={\left(1\right)}^{2}-2⋅1⋅2i+(2{i)}^{2}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007aaf87f1-fca8-479c-a499-c4d2debc794f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017aaf87f1-fca8-479c-a499-c4d2de