                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000080e34ea2-7a46-4160-8257-c0c3878bb871" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\sum α=α+β+γ=0;\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000180e34ea2-7a46-4160-8257-c0c3878bb871"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000080e34ea2-7a46-4160-8257-c0c3878bb871 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000180e34ea2-7a46-4160-8257-c0c3878bb871 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000006278696f-480a-43b0-bc4e-59c4ff566cd6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\sum αβ=αβ+βγ+γα=+\frac{b}{a}\ ;αβγ=-\frac{c}{a};\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000016278696f-480a-43b0-bc4e-59c4ff566cd6"><sub> </sub></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006278696f-480a-43b0-bc4e-59c4ff566cd6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016278696f-480a-43b0-bc4e-59c4ff566cd6 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003e833476-5683-4d45-b5ee-bef9a5a73d56" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\sum {α}^{2}{β}^{2}={\left(\sum αβ\right)}^{2}-2αβγ\times \sum α={\left(\frac{b}{a}\right)}^{2}-2.\left(-\frac{c}{a}\right).0=\frac{{b}^{2}}{{a}^{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013e833476-5683-4d45-b5ee-bef9a5a73d56"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013e833476-5683-4d45-b5ee-bef9a5a73d56"><sub> </sub></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003e833476-5683-4d45-b5ee-bef9a5a73d56 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: