                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000094888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5">awi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5">, </span><span class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5">mvaviY</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5"> </span><span class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5">g~j</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(α\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5"> </span><span class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5">Zvn‡j</span><span class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5">,</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({α}^{2}+pα+q=0\ ;\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000094888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000194888257-4927-45f1-a87f-175b8581fba5 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000d26e76ac-3c34-4616-b022-c13453fee0f5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({α}^{2}+mα+c=0∴\ \frac{{α}^{2}}{pc-mq}=\frac{α}{q-c}=\frac{1}{m-p}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d26e76ac-3c34-4616-b022-c13453fee0f5"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d26e76ac-3c34-4616-b022-c13453fee0f5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt