                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318">awi</span><span class="pt-000001b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318">, &#175;</span><span class="pt-000001b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318">&#250;k</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318">&#169;‡Ki </span><span class="pt-000001b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318">mgxKiY</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(3x-y+k=0∴y=3x+k\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b62b3fc9-0e7a-45a1-b4f5-58a9325fe318 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000f20c681-0000-40ef-b181-076818ece855" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000010f20c681-0000-40ef-b181-076818ece855">kZ&#169;g‡Z</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010f20c681-0000-40ef-b181-076818ece855">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({\left(3x+k\right)}^{2}-36x-10\left(3x+k\right)+97=0\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000f20c681-0000-40ef-b181-076818ece855 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010f20c681-0000-40ef-b181-076818ece855 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ad1c68ee-b837-4274-95b9-df3650ada7cd" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴9{x}^{2}+x\left(6k-66\right)+{k