                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000bccf37a2-9c30-4612-9e27-5c83a6e9cf30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(5{x}^{2}+15x-10y-4=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001bccf37a2-9c30-4612-9e27-5c83a6e9cf30"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000bccf37a2-9c30-4612-9e27-5c83a6e9cf30 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001bccf37a2-9c30-4612-9e27-5c83a6e9cf30 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005c2acb04-e046-4f0b-bfcd-2f61cfe51cb4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒5\left({x}^{2}+2.\frac{3}{2}x+\frac{9}{4}\right)=10y+4+\frac{45}{4}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015c2acb04-e046-4f0b-bfcd-2f61cfe51cb4"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005c2acb04-e046-4f0b-bfcd-2f61cfe51cb4 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000015c2acb04-e046-4f0b-bfcd-2f61cfe51cb4 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003477e8cf-32d3-4176-82f3-201a6c0a42f5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{\left(x+\frac{3}{2}\right)}^{2}=\frac{10}{5}\left(y+\frac{61}{40}\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013477e8cf-32d3-4176-82f3-201a6c0a42f5"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003477e8cf-32d3-4176-82f3-201a6c0a42f5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013477e8cf-32d3-4176-82f3-201a6c0a42f5 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</st