                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">awi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">, </span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">e</span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">„</span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">n`v</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">&#182; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x\) </span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">-</span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">A&#182; Ges &#182;</span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">z`&#170;v</span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">&#182;</span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\ y\) </span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">-</span><span class="pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377">A&#182;|</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001fdae71e7-9312-4a1a-a501-31106d6ff377 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cd6b903d-6ea6-4220-97d1-8563a4cec432" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\frac{2{b}^{2}}{a}=\frac{1}{2}\times 2a⇒\frac{{b}^{2}}{{a}^{2}}=\frac{1}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cd6b903d-6ea6-4220-97d1-8563a4cec432"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cd6b903d-6ea6-4220-97d1