                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000037720020-55cc-4046-8374-cd9368a929bb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sin\ {{tan}^{-1}\ {cot\ {{cosec}^{-1}\ {x}}}}=sin\ {{tan}^{-1}\ {cot\ {{cot}^{-1}\ {\sqrt{{x}^{2}-1}}}}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000137720020-55cc-4046-8374-cd9368a929bb"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000037720020-55cc-4046-8374-cd9368a929bb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000137720020-55cc-4046-8374-cd9368a929bb {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003846722a-338b-4e7c-b5e2-ec3aec9eff8f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=sin\ {{tan}^{-1}\ {\sqrt{{x}^{2}-1}}}=sin\ {{sin}^{-1}\ {\frac{\sqrt{{x}^{2}-1}}{x}}}=\frac{\sqrt{{x}^{2}-1}}{x}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013846722a-338b-4e7c-b5e2-ec3aec9eff8f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003846722a-338b-4e7c-b5e2-ec3aec9eff8f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013846722a-338b-4e7c-b5e2-ec3aec9eff8f {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
