                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000fa774409-e923-4c90-99f1-e9b747765e08" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\sqrt{3}sin\ {θ}+cos\ {θ=\sqrt{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fa774409-e923-4c90-99f1-e9b747765e08"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000fa774409-e923-4c90-99f1-e9b747765e08 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001fa774409-e923-4c90-99f1-e9b747765e08 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000fa66f7bc-62d7-49f7-aaeb-505f369a9f6c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}sin\ {θ}+\frac{1}{2}cos\ {θ=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fa66f7bc-62d7-49f7-aaeb-505f369a9f6c"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000fa66f7bc-62d7-49f7-aaeb-505f369a9f6c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001fa66f7bc-62d7-49f7-aaeb-505f369a9f6c {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000016cb47af-f1a8-4753-b31d-3229153e9195" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒cos\ {\frac{π}{6}}sin\ {θ+sin\ {\frac{π}{6}cos\ {θ=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000116cb47af-f1a8-4753-b31d-3229153e9195"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000016cb47af-f1a8-4753-b31d-3229153e9195 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000116cb47af-f1a8-4753-b31d-3229153e9195 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000b651335-788c-4c2a-ba7d-e7247c1abb77" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒sin\ {\left(θ+\frac{π}{6}\right)=sin\ {\frac{π}{4}}}⇒θ+\frac{π}{6}=\frac{π}{4}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010b651335-788c-4c2a-ba7d-e7247c1abb77"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000b651335-788c-4c2a-ba7d-e7247c1abb77 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010b651335-788c-4c2a-ba7d-e7247c1abb77 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000dc30f809-8a73-42d7-857f-e18edbeaec51" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒θ=\frac{π}{4}-\frac{π}{6}=\frac{3π-2π}{12}=\frac{π}{12}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001dc30f809-8a73-42d7-857f-e18edbeaec51"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000dc30f809-8a73-42d7-857f-e18edbeaec51 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001dc30f809-8a73-42d7-857f-e18edbeaec51 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
