                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000fe7be8f5-8869-4fe1-8547-bf69ea3ab32d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(cose{c}^{2}\left({tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{2}}+{sin}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{\sqrt{10}}}\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fe7be8f5-8869-4fe1-8547-bf69ea3ab32d"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000fe7be8f5-8869-4fe1-8547-bf69ea3ab32d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001fe7be8f5-8869-4fe1-8547-bf69ea3ab32d {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000012ded1fb-37dc-4cef-a5a3-c13d97e59822" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=cose{c}^{2}\left({tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{2}}+{tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{3}}\right)=cose{c}^{2}\left(\frac{π}{4}\right)=2\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000112ded1fb-37dc-4cef-a5a3-c13d97e59822"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000012ded1fb-37dc-4cef-a5a3-c13d97e59822 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000112ded1fb-37dc-4cef-a5a3-c13d97e59822 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
