                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000000174ce06-5286-4782-8401-82b1023dfac9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{R}{{R}^{{'}}}=\frac{sin⁡(α-{θ}^{{'}})}{sin⁡(α-θ)}⇒\frac{6}{6\sqrt{3}}=\frac{sin⁡(110^{\circ} -{θ}^{{'}})}{sin⁡(110^{\circ} -50^{\circ} )}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010174ce06-5286-4782-8401-82b1023dfac9"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000174ce06-5286-4782-8401-82b1023dfac9 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010174ce06-5286-4782-8401-82b1023dfac9 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007b3f748f-338c-407e-b0b7-06e31fd92a34" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒sin\ {\left(110^{\circ} -{θ}^{{'}}\right)}=\frac{1}{2}⇒110^{\circ} -{θ}^{{'}}=30^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017b3f748f-338c-407e-b0b7-06e31fd92a34"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007b3f748f-338c-407e-b0b7-06e31fd92a34 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017b3f748f-338c-407e-b0b7-06e31fd92a34 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000371df893-39c9-4519-9838-6980bb68fd1e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴{θ}^{{'}}=80^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001371df893-39c9-4519-9838-6980bb68fd1e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000371df893-39c9-4519-9838-6980bb68fd1e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001371df893-39c9-4519-9838-6980bb68fd1e {font-family: 