                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000020aa2e57-0fb9-452c-95b0-01556de210e5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000120aa2e57-0fb9-452c-95b0-01556de210e5"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.6319018in;height: 0.9670013in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000020aa2e57-0fb9-452c-95b0-01556de210e5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000120aa2e57-0fb9-452c-95b0-01556de210e5 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000086831406-e8fa-4509-af0d-9d48ee6fc0b1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(l=2a\ ;\ \frac{T}{l+a}=\frac{W}{\sqrt{{\left(l+a\right)}^{2}-{a}^{2}}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000186831406-e8fa-4509-af0d-9d48ee6fc0b1"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000086831406-e8fa-4509-af0d-9d48ee6fc0b1 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000186831406-e8fa-4509-af0d-9d48ee6fc0b1 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003cc7ef38-68cd-4ceb-a869-f79e776b95d7" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒T=W\times \frac{l+a}{\sqrt{{l}^{2}+2al}}=4\times \frac{2a+a}{\sqrt{{\left(2a\right)}^{2}+2a(2a)}}N=4\times \frac{3}{\sqrt{8}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013cc7ef38-68cd-4ceb-a869-f79e776b95d7"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003cc7ef38-68cd-4ceb-a869-f79e776b95d7 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013cc7ef38-68cd-4ceb-a869-f79e776b95d7 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="p